1
00:00:16,298 --> 00:00:17,019
Hold it tight.

2
00:00:18,279 --> 00:00:18,738
Okay.

3
00:00:18,738 --> 00:00:19,199
How's it going?

4
00:00:20,538 --> 00:00:21,279
Let me see yours.

5
00:00:22,679 --> 00:00:25,879
You haven't done this valve well.

6
00:00:26,478 --> 00:00:27,419
Let me do it for you.

7
00:00:30,978 --> 00:00:31,858
It's so itchy.

8
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:39,478
It's enough to witness her happiness.

9
00:00:42,679 --> 00:00:43,418
Something happened.

10
00:00:44,198 --> 00:00:46,499
Miss Ye and Mr. Wu have not been found.

11
00:00:46,978 --> 00:00:47,439
Hurry up.

12
00:01:39,399 --> 00:01:41,498
Zhi Mei, wake up.

13
00:01:58,539 --> 00:02:00,319
Zhi Mei, you're awake.

14
00:02:02,539 --> 00:02:03,599
Is that you?

15
00:02:30,419 --> 00:02:32,079
Do you two remember the date

16
00:02:32,119 --> 00:02:33,619
when you first fell in love with each other?

17
00:02:35,338 --> 00:02:36,619
It should be

18
00:02:37,158 --> 00:02:37,998
March 20th.

19
00:02:38,438 --> 00:02:39,158
It was a weekend.

20
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:40,979
You must have the wrong date.

21
00:02:41,498 --> 00:02:43,299
It was August 21st.

22
00:02:43,438 --> 00:02:45,338
The date of our first official date.

23
00:02:45,459 --> 00:02:46,079
You forgot?

24
00:02:46,459 --> 00:02:47,778
The dates don't match.

25
00:02:47,778 --> 00:02:49,399
Looks like there's a story.

26
00:02:51,038 --> 00:02:52,838
I fell for you first.

27
00:02:53,658 --> 00:02:54,859
I noticed you

28
00:02:54,859 --> 00:02:55,818
from the moment you started school.

29
00:02:56,658 --> 00:02:57,699
But back then,

30
00:02:58,519 --> 00:02:59,818
I wasn't even in your sights.

31
00:03:01,338 --> 00:03:02,679
Secret love turned real.

32
00:03:02,679 --> 00:03:03,799
So romantic.

33
00:03:04,119 --> 00:03:04,598
So, Mr. Wu,

34
00:03:05,119 --> 00:03:06,519
what's the most romantic thing

35
00:03:06,519 --> 00:03:07,679
you did to win over

36
00:03:07,679 --> 00:03:09,299
President Ye in college?

37
00:03:10,399 --> 00:03:12,278
He folded a tree of paper cranes for me.

38
00:03:12,838 --> 00:03:13,938
At that time,

39
00:03:14,119 --> 00:03:15,199
I was really, really moved.

40
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:16,979
Yes,

41
00:03:17,619 --> 00:03:18,818
I folded them all night.

42
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:20,558
I think it was worth it

43
00:03:20,558 --> 00:03:21,558
to see you smile

44
00:03:22,679 --> 00:03:23,338
at that moment.

45
00:03:24,519 --> 00:03:26,359
Your love is truly amazing.

46
00:03:28,619 --> 00:03:29,158
Sir,

47
00:03:29,558 --> 00:03:30,919
you've done so much for her,

48
00:03:30,919 --> 00:03:31,919
even got involved in a lawsuit.

49
00:03:32,399 --> 00:03:33,558
But look at her,

50
00:03:33,818 --> 00:03:35,079
showing off her love with someone else.

51
00:03:35,959 --> 00:03:38,119
If this is your final choice,

52
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:39,538
at least

53
00:03:40,318 --> 00:03:41,639
I can still clear away

54
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,998
the last danger for you.

55
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,119
Zhimei,

56
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:56,619
I feel like we're

57
00:03:56,619 --> 00:03:57,438
back to the old days.

58
00:03:58,658 --> 00:03:59,718
Thank you for giving me

59
00:03:59,718 --> 00:04:00,498
the chance to continue loving you.

60
00:04:03,258 --> 00:04:04,799
The voiceprint comparison results are in.

61
00:04:07,119 --> 00:04:08,538
It's confirmed to be Zhou Xubai's voice.

62
00:04:10,859 --> 00:04:12,019
He's completely ruthless.

63
00:04:13,119 --> 00:04:13,658
Zhi Mei,

64
00:04:14,378 --> 00:04:15,079
I swear,

65
00:04:15,658 --> 00:04:16,579
I'll never let him...

66
00:04:16,579 --> 00:04:17,239
I mean,

67
00:04:18,818 --> 00:04:20,619
the recording on my phone

68
00:04:21,058 --> 00:04:21,679
is from Zhou Xubai.

69
00:04:26,859 --> 00:04:28,239
During the interview,

70
00:04:28,698 --> 00:04:29,719
I said I received

71
00:04:29,719 --> 00:04:30,898
many origami cranes in college.

72
00:04:32,799 --> 00:04:34,378
Actually, they were from Zhou Xubai.

73
00:04:36,359 --> 00:04:36,919
But you

74
00:04:39,398 --> 00:04:41,039
never did that.

75
00:04:42,779 --> 00:04:43,679
No, Zhimei.

76
00:04:43,679 --> 00:04:45,058
It's been too long.

77
00:04:45,359 --> 00:04:46,138
I forgot it.

78
00:04:46,138 --> 00:04:46,818
Until now,

79
00:04:49,359 --> 00:04:50,398
I'd rather believe

80
00:04:50,398 --> 00:04:51,898
you really got it wrong.

81
00:04:52,958 --> 00:04:54,659
But voiceprint comparison can't be faked.

82
00:04:54,998 --> 00:04:56,359
Your voice is

83
00:04:56,539 --> 00:04:57,659
so similar to Zhou Xubai's.

84
00:04:58,758 --> 00:05:00,479
It's like you're the same person.

85
00:05:02,119 --> 00:05:05,039
So, you're the one who talked to the killer

86
00:05:05,698 --> 00:05:07,398
and hired him to make an accident.

87
00:05:14,119 --> 00:05:15,339
And the one

88
00:05:15,339 --> 00:05:16,779
who accompanied me

89
00:05:18,018 --> 00:05:18,679
through the hardest time

90
00:05:20,739 --> 00:05:21,558
was Zhou Xubai.

91
00:05:25,378 --> 00:05:26,479
It was never you.

92
00:05:30,039 --> 00:05:31,039
It was never you.

93
00:05:31,119 --> 00:05:32,138
It was me.

94
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:36,779
I'm sorry.

95
00:05:37,679 --> 00:05:38,578
I'm sorry, Zhimei.

96
00:05:39,679 --> 00:05:40,938
I just love you too much.

97
00:05:43,378 --> 00:05:44,839
We were just one step away

98
00:05:46,558 --> 00:05:47,659
from being happy forever.

99
00:05:53,898 --> 00:05:54,958
Why did this happen?

100
00:05:56,119 --> 00:05:56,898
Why?

101
00:05:59,119 --> 00:06:00,318
When did I

102
00:06:02,438 --> 00:06:04,159
lose you completely?

103
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:15,318
Who told you to do this?

104
00:06:30,679 --> 00:06:31,159
Zhi Mei.

105
00:06:31,739 --> 00:06:32,719
Zhou Xubai just delivered a document

106
00:06:32,719 --> 00:06:33,299
for you.

107
00:06:33,859 --> 00:06:34,698
He seems

108
00:06:34,938 --> 00:06:36,799
ready to leave for good.

109
00:06:40,119 --> 00:06:40,599
Zhimei.

110
00:06:42,638 --> 00:06:43,498
I'm begging you.

111
00:06:44,479 --> 00:06:45,659
Please.

112
00:06:45,938 --> 00:06:46,599
Don't go.

113
00:06:52,318 --> 00:06:53,758
I've missed him

114
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:57,058
too many times because of you.

115
00:07:01,239 --> 00:07:01,739
This time,

116
00:07:03,119 --> 00:07:04,078
I won't miss him again.

117
00:07:08,578 --> 00:07:09,299
Zhimei.

118
00:07:09,638 --> 00:07:11,279
Don't go.

119
00:07:12,698 --> 00:07:14,818
Zhimei.

120
00:07:32,359 --> 00:07:35,518
Has Mr. Zhou checked out?

121
00:07:35,518 --> 00:07:37,599
He just left five minutes ago.

122
00:07:58,099 --> 00:08:00,898
Answer the phone, why don't you answer the phone?

123
00:08:05,878 --> 00:08:06,659
Zhou Xubai,

124
00:08:08,398 --> 00:08:09,638
where are you?

125
00:08:13,758 --> 00:08:14,719
Zhou Xubai,

126
00:08:15,698 --> 00:08:17,279
where are you?

127
00:08:20,998 --> 00:08:22,719
Why don't you answer the phone?

128
00:08:31,919 --> 00:08:33,378
Zhou Xubai,

129
00:08:34,818 --> 00:08:37,239
where are you?

130
00:08:40,199 --> 00:08:42,459
I can't find him.

131
00:09:05,859 --> 00:09:06,439
Zhi Mei.

132
00:09:25,898 --> 00:09:27,018
Zhou Xubai,

133
00:09:28,018 --> 00:09:29,778
why don't you answer the phone?

134
00:09:35,178 --> 00:09:36,418
It's out of power.

135
00:09:40,979 --> 00:09:41,898
I know everything.

136
00:09:43,479 --> 00:09:44,758
From the past to the present,

137
00:09:46,138 --> 00:09:47,739
the person who has always been by my side

138
00:09:48,319 --> 00:09:49,119
is you.

139
00:09:53,758 --> 00:09:55,378
The person I like

140
00:09:56,758 --> 00:09:58,138
is also you.

141
00:10:02,219 --> 00:10:03,798
It's always been you.

142
00:10:22,178 --> 00:10:23,459
Thank you.

143
00:10:36,739 --> 00:10:37,819
Can I

144
00:10:38,579 --> 00:10:39,959
hear your voice?

145
00:10:40,579 --> 00:10:41,579
Just for a moment.

146
00:10:47,439 --> 00:10:47,918
Hello.

147
00:10:57,599 --> 00:10:59,079
Your world is shattered,

148
00:11:00,619 --> 00:11:01,898
and I'll pick up the pieces.

149
00:11:03,378 --> 00:11:04,339
From now on,

150
00:11:05,719 --> 00:11:06,758
your future

151
00:11:08,298 --> 00:11:08,918
has me.

152
00:11:13,119 --> 00:11:13,619
I'm sorry.

153
00:11:14,099 --> 00:11:15,339
It's all my fault.

154
00:11:15,778 --> 00:11:17,859
I shouldn't have let you

155
00:11:18,138 --> 00:11:19,079
go through so much hardship alone

156
00:11:19,658 --> 00:11:21,479
and wait for me for so long.

157
00:11:27,378 --> 00:11:28,619
So now,

158
00:11:28,998 --> 00:11:30,378
do you still want

159
00:11:31,158 --> 00:11:32,278
to be with me?

160
00:11:32,819 --> 00:11:33,979
I've been waiting for this day

161
00:11:34,739 --> 00:11:35,959
for a long time.
